</ul>

<h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ol>
    <li><strong>Order Fulfillment:</strong> process and deliver your purchases.</li>
    <li><strong>Communication:</strong> order updates and service notices.</li>
    <li><strong>Marketing:</strong> optional promotional emails (you can opt out anytime).</li>
    <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> improve site performance and features.</li>
</ol>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this policy, please contact us.</p>

